public class WordsSearchTrie
extends java.lang.Object
implements Trie

Implementation of Trie used for searching words from dictionary with wild card (?) characters The difference in the implementation of this trie is that there are as many tries as the number of size of words for e.g. words bank and banks will be in two different tries
